    CPTAC Ovarian Cancer Proteomics Dataset

    oca.set.Rd

    Processed iTRAQ data from both PNNL and JHU sites.

    data("cptac_oca")

    Format

    An MSnSet with 8103 features and 73 samples.

    Source

    CPTAC study

    pData

    A data frame consisting of 73 rows (samples) and 39 columns:

    Tumor.Nuclei

    Percent of cells in the tissue sample with tumor nuclei.

    Necrosis

    Percent of tumor nuclei that are necrotic.

    PNNL.Weight..mg.

    Weight of the non-tumor tissue in milligrams.

    Residual.Tumor.Tissue..mg.

    Weight of the tumor tissue in milligrams.

    TSS
    primary_therapy_outcome_success

    One of "COMPLETE.RESPONSE", "STABLE.DISEASE", or "PROGRESSIVE.DISEASE".

    days_to_death

    Days between

    Platinum.Refractory
    tumor_grade
    tumor_residual_disease
    tumor_stage

    Tumor stage.

    anatomic_organ_subdivision

    Either "left", "right", or "bilateral".

    days_to_birth

    Negative age (in days) of subject.

    days_to_tumor_recurrence

    Days before first tumor recurrence.

    race

    The race of the subject.

    site_of_tumor_first_recurrence

    "LOCO.REGIONAL" or "METASTASIS".

    Batch

    The sample batch.

    additional_chemo_therapy

    "YES" if the subject received additional chemotherapy; "NO" otherwise.

    additional_drug_therapy

    "YES" if the subject received additional drug therapy; "NO" otherwise.

    additional_pharmaceutical_therapy

    "YES" if the subject received additional pharmaceutical therapy; "NO" otherwise.

    additional_radiation_therapy

    "YES" if the subject received additional radiation therapy; "NO" otherwise.

    targeted_molecular_therapy

    "YES" if the subject received targeted molecular therapy; "NO" otherwise.

    year_of_initial_pathologic_diagnosis

    The year when subjects were first diagnosed with ovarian cancer.

    iTRAQ_Batch

    The iTRAQ batch identifier.

    iTRAQ_ID
    ReporterIon
    SUBTYPE

    Ovarian cancer subtype. Either "Differentiated", "Immunoreactive", "Mesenchymal", or "Proliferative".

    AGE

    Subject age in years.

    PLATINUM.STATUS

    The tumor's response to platinum therapy. Either "SENSITIVE" or "RESISTANT".

    TUMORRESIDUALDISEASE
    SURVIVALSTATUS

    The survival status of the patient. Either "LIVING" or "DECEASED".

    SURVIVALMONTHS
    RECURRENCE.MONTHS
    Differentiated.binary

    TRUE if SUBTYPE is "Differentiated"; FALSE otherwise.

    Immunoreactive.binary

    TRUE if SUBTYPE is "Immunoreactive"; FALSE otherwise.

    Mesenchymal.binary

    TRUE if SUBTYPE is "Mesenchymal"; FALSE otherwise.

    Proliferative.binary

    TRUE if SUBTYPE is "Proliferative"; FALSE otherwise.

    SILHOUETTE.WIDTH
    fake

    fData

    RefSeq

    The NCBI reference sequence.

    Examples

    data("cptac_oca")
